am at the recently-concluded 2024 Paris Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philadelphia_76ers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.528108879646433e-64, \"text\": \"Philadelphia 76ers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philadelphia_76ers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philadelphia_76ers\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 1.1317290936992643e-11, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}, {\"begin\": 546, \"end\": 566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8185366812232706, \"rank\": 0.22084504940845565, \"text\": \"French national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yabusele was drafted by the Boston Celtics with the 16th pick in 2016, and made 74 appearances for the team across the 2017-18 and 2018-19 seasons.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 650, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1247693268928675e-61, \"text\": \"Boston Celtics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he was waived after averaging just 2.3 points and 6.6 minutes per game.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The power forward spent the 2016-17 season in the Chinese Basketball Association (CBA) with the Shanghai Sharks, averaging 21.5 points and 9.5 rebounds per outing.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.643999224116275e-69, \"text\": \"Chinese Basketball Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai_Sharks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shanghai Sharks\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai_Sharks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai_Sharks\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He briefly returned to the CBA during the 2019-20 campaign, playing in 15 games with the Nanjing Monkey Kings.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1038, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.892109225186881e-14, \"text\": \"CBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nanjing_Tongxi_Monkey_Kings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nanjing Monkey Kings\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nanjing_Tongxi_Monkey_Kings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nanjing_Tongxi_Monkey_Kings\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yabusele started his professional career in 2014 and spent two seasons at French LNB Pro A club Rouen.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.769629913574618, \"rank\": 0.29673355955742586, \"tex